            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1918.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa fillets</strong>, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 2 min on each side or until cooked through and lightly crisp – this is your<strong> crispy fried fish</strong></p>",
